data.description: Hurry you don't want to miss this! This home is perfect for country living with almost 15 ACRES of sweeping mountain views, rolling pastures, and a river that runs along the property. Outside you have mature trees, garden spaces, a duck pond, outbuildings, the list goes on and on. Located in Matlock you have the convenience of shopping, schools, and hospitals near by but also in your own private oasis. There is so much potential in this property with the possibility of subdivision. You have to see it to believe it!
